Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看見痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.12,0:00:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是空虛地渡過每一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.66,0:00:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在充滿消沉心情的城市裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在優美地閃耀着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NCarry On！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.07,0:00:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要灰心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NShinin Oh！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.01,0:00:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被破壞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.65,0:00:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成愛啊，\N像把宇宙包裏一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.42,0:01:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.73,0:01:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索等人的舒勒隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功消滅了比列騰艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但當胡索聼到\N露比施羅的聲音後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.39,0:01:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被迷住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.49,0:01:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，\N進入了凱羅天使空域的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.77,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被聖軍事同盟艦隊\N被鈴聲所包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.20,0:01:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰場的彗星花娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終組合看來已完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信它還未\N能完全發揮功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.47,0:02:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只得這種規模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使要發揮預定的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信還須要一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能一口氣衝破比列騰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.24,0:02:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫托拉度艦隊防衛線，\N真失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多些地球聯邦軍的\N增援就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是卑斯柏防衛陣勢\N比想像中利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們前面有達斯羅的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有莫托拉度艦隊的\N殘餘部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.29,0:02:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而杜根艦隊\N在後方保護凱羅天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那部巨大的\N飛碟型機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.47,0:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聼聞鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是從那部\N機動戰士傳出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也從凱羅天使的\N空域傳出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麽巨大的東西\N進入了地球圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某處的殖民衛星\N應該會探測到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.56,0:03:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多來往木星\N和地球的船隊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.03,0:03:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些船隊\N把建造凱羅天使的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,材料分解運送吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方舍.卡格持\N是由木星歸來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，我也聼聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整頓[希寧三號] 的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建立了木星聯合共和國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你年紀雖小，\N但這是很好的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直當我是其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要咬到何時呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對暴力！反對體罰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索在生甚麽氣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素芝，拜託你照顧卡魯曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的態度很冷淡，真怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領袖有很多事要做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.44,0:04:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和卡沙尼里亞時\N不同是當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男性是不能坦白的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小說裡也有寫過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的爸爸也是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要任性！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是能和爸爸一起戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.03,0:04:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要感謝上天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我明白…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.47,0:04:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索的爸爸以\N占.撤哈林之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和聯邦軍的大人物周旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要獨力領導\N神聖軍事同盟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，你竟然發脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知足及任性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和連賀斯J r的\N冒牌貨不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.85,0:04:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.42,0:04:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何要等候命令！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使飛碟型\N機動戰士發出鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是也已經準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應付那部\N機動戰士的盾牌嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被真的占.撤哈林刺激了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他殖民衛星也有援軍來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼昂列度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人想勝過\N珍路.達古的占啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以米加雷射盾\N為中心的作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你說多少遍也好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，占.撤哈林大人的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不能違抗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡里路，入來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是連賀斯Jr的占.撤哈林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令出擊的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都估到的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌貨的出擊命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒理由會跟來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭中要斷絕父子關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次作戰的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.48,0:05:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要消滅凱羅天使\N周邊的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有父子分為敵我戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓連賀斯J r發施號令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也就能保存他的體面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該稍為讓兒子覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似一個爸爸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使將軍你對我那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其他將軍並不是那樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的憂慮，\N但你過慮了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟舒勒隊，\N由加，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅，湯馬殊，要出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我有苗娜一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，你有莎蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？很興奮和舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是卡沙尼里亞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跌下去怎辦呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信爸爸嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.05,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，\N可以借那個盾給我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.52,0:07:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會比你運用得更好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以為我情緒低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.79,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就估錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有類似偵察機物體接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，艾賓，出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！那傢伙真好性！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅，我們幫他是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的任務是掩護啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我以胡索\N為中心作戰嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒人做中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不能進行組織戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無道理就是無道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索不一定是最好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由加小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然在敵人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用無線電說過不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要對話就要把機體接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用機外線路通話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是要人照顧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在戰場上可以猶疑嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聼到那個細路的振翅聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要喧嘩！花娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.67,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那班少年是被你引來宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是班可愛的細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你濫用了贊歷古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在說新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是那個操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放出翼之光的高達的細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比他更利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會收拾神聖軍事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令達斯羅你能\N去到凱羅天使啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想我那樣做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會成全你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.21,0:09:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你替我發射\N贊歷古的雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.95,0:09:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有副座位嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部機當然有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你只要操縱成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.24,0:09:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像個女人在操縱就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.34,0:09:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷射砲要瞄準白色傢伙發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在這距離識別…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在識別敵我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在…這種距離…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,張開心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傾聼在宇宙迴響的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2.2度上方0.01
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.17,0:10:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好像是瞄準我射來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索的V2！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了，美愛娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事呢，又會射來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要瞄準的就瞄準我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和預計一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,細路出來了，去 知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V2也有長距離雷射砲的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他開始焦急追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我令他再焦急一點\N知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雷射砲我的機動力會下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.91,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了！花娜少校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷射砲的起動有問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我信賴的機師，基爾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還未被擊中啊，細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣好像只會\N中了敵人的圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把我當細路般戲弄！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人放棄戰鬥！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算投降嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！不是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麽！？這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那裡的機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.17,0:12:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我在港口市鎮\N遇到的那個細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙做甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.24,0:12:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你也知道我嘗過的恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.88,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受宇宙漂流刑時的恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我發瘋的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.19,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願割破太空衣\N一死了之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花娜少校，你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是甚麽人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是達斯羅.華歌上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令我們來救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他判我接受\N宇宙漂流刑的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校那樣做是為了\N瞞騙格諾古、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡格持和杜根等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.55,0:13:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅有計劃要趕走卡格持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個計劃被發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和胡索等人一起\N被送上斷頭台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何要處死我！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為高達部隊的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅逃過斬頭之刑失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而卡格持想再度利用達斯羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替他保護凱羅天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人物所做的事真沉悶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得在宇宙\N整整漂流了兩日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的會攻擊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花娜原來想這樣做嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊由我來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有機師在裡面嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有受傷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來！  知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被米加粒子砲\N一顆粒子擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類也會立即死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太多說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是麥哲的替身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.10,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有盾牌你能打贏我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是細路的援軍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍也來幫手嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差少少我就成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然來阻住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用雷射砲收拾你們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦軍哪支部隊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機師你還生存嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事！\N你們屬於哪支部隊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.43,0:15:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍路.達古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍路.達古！是爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直看着我的戰鬥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！\N我還像細路般情緒低落！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們發射上身部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\N把所有下身部份也射出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做甚麽？胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用麥捷先生的戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有後備盾牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍路.達古的部隊也在苦戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索好像有妙計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正規武器也沒有\N怎樣戰鬥呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.74,0:15:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要聼我的說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！現在是戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快準備發射上身和下身部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，射出上身部份後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連續射出下身部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索又有妙計呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.86,0:16:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結合，好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下身部份發射！去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連續發射V2的\N下身部份！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要下身部份的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的也可以使用，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.85,0:16:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌莉小姐你掩護我就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是用大量\N下身部份的戰術？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是拉京的麥捷.穫加先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用過的戰術呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸收別人長處\N並立即運用是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那種戰術\N他是第一次使用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索打算去對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發出鈴聲的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩護胡索，知道嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.46,0:17:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！細路！又來娛樂我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下身部份衝過去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,細路沒有還擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.99,0:17:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西真討厭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.53,0:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,細路在哪裡！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V高達！！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.25,0:18:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斷頭台的鈴聲\N就不會響起吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花娜小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不了結我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斷頭台的鈴聲\N永遠也會響起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊歷古的識別訊號消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫機動戰士部隊離開射線軸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅艦隊前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅神聖軍事同盟的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有第二輪飛彈接近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有自己人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，得不到支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.93,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採用迴避高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航路怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐！\N這樣下去不行的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們潛入凱羅天使的空域吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啊，莎蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟正遠離艦砲的射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有瑪貝德小姐在指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我有種\N非常討厭的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？莎蒂叫我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，你要衝入敵陣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要組成陣形就發出指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在單獨行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它正漂向凱羅天使\N附近的空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以白色方舟的戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛進敵人中心的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有死路一條！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.99,0:19:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以不顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有艾莉莎在的白色方舟嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的主力出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速前進！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再追來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在本艦周圍的\N只有舒勒隊！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟正漂向\N凱羅天使附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年部隊去了追它嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再追過去會有危險的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着就…交由穆巴勒司令…\N指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那沒問題，但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不理那班細路行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，即使只得他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.88,0:20:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們都會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒事吧！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.59,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真實的凱羅天使吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還有一段距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但形狀能清楚看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱羅天使…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.76,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過吧！花娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麽啊，我沒有死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.10,0:21:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘艦還有很多機動戰士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦隊也已像樣地\N進行了砲擊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並引了神聖軍事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到凱羅天使附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.38,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該在凱羅天使的\N卡格持和杜根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在發抖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.22,0:22:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.18,0:22:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在銀色的海上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.18,0:22:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灼熱的波浪湧上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.29,0:22:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到跪下的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.06,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變成說話，\N只是你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.54,0:23:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能變得優美就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.34,0:23:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次TENDERNESS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.48,0:23:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的内心在月亮的菱鏡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.55,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着閃耀的未來在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.32,0:23:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次和你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.69,0:23:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你的瞳孔顯出孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.17,0:23:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了令戰事不再擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.81,0:23:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定和媽媽瑪利亞見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.11,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那產生出誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.45,0:23:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到兩名相愛的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.12,0:23:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雷射劍互相\N刺穿對方的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.42,0:23:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回，機動戰士V高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.03,0:23:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛在光的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收看吧
